# Typography Guidelines

## Font Families

### Primary Heading Font: Pano Bold Trial
All headings (h1-h6) and display text MUST use **Pano Bold Trial** (PanoTrial).

**Applied to:**
- `.hero__headline` - Hero section headlines
- `.section-title` - Section titles
- `.program__content h3` - Program section headings
- `.pillars__content h2` - Pillars section headings
- `.about__content h2` - About section headings
- `.brand` - Site logo/branding
- `h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6` - All semantic heading elements

**Font stack:**
```css
font-family: PanoTrial, Montserrat, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial;
```

**Font files location:**
```
public/fonts/
├── HW Pano Trial Bold.woff2
├── HW Pano Trial Bold.woff
└── HW Pano Trial Bold.otf
```

### Body Font: Montserrat
Body text uses Montserrat with system font fallbacks.

## Font Sizes

### Fixed Sizes (52px)
These elements use a fixed 52px font size:
- `.hero__headline` - Hero headline
- `.program__content h3` - Program section headers

### Responsive Sizes
Other headings use `clamp()` for responsive sizing:
- `.section-title`: `clamp(28px, 5vw, 72px)`
- `.about__content h2`: `clamp(32px, 5vw, 64px)`

## Color Palette

### Brand Colors
- **Primary/Accent**: `#E8FF3B` (lime green) - used for highlights
- **Secondary**: `#E8FF3B` (same as primary)

### Text Colors
- **Light sections**: `#1f2a2d` (dark gray)
- **Dark sections**: `#e8edef` (light gray) or `#fff` (white)
- **Muted text**: `#6a7679`

## Example Usage

```css
/* Good - All headings use PanoTrial */
.new-section h2 {
  font-family: PanoTrial, Montserrat, system-ui;
  font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 64px);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #fff;
}

/* Bad - Missing PanoTrial font */
.new-section h2 {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}
```

## Rules
1. ✅ ALWAYS use PanoTrial for all headings and display text
2. ✅ Maintain the full font-family stack with fallbacks
3. ✅ Use 52px for hero and program headers
4. ✅ Use clamp() for responsive section headings
5. ❌ NEVER use system fonts alone for headings
6. ❌ NEVER remove PanoTrial from the font stack
